---
// portfolio.astro — hidden, no layout, noindex everywhere
// Do NOT link to this page from any nav, footer, or other page.
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Eric Chan — Selected Work</title>

  <!-- ─── Bot & crawler protection ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow, noarchive, nosnippet, noimageindex" />
  <meta name="googlebot" content="noindex, nofollow, noarchive, nosnippet, noimageindex" />
  <meta name="bingbot" content="noindex, nofollow" />

  <!-- ─── Fonts (matching Inlet Wire) ──────────────────────────────────── -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Montserrat:wght@900&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />

  <style>
    /* ── Design tokens — exact Inlet Wire palette ───────────────────────── */
    :root {
      --ink:          #0A0A0A;
      --paper:        #FFFFFF;
      --cream:        #F5F1EC;
      --muted:        #5A5A5A;
      --rule:         #E8E8E8;
      --font-display: "Montserrat", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      --font-body:    "Inter", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      --maxw:         1120px;
    }

    /* ── Reset ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body, h1, h2, h3, h4, p, ul, ol, li, figure, blockquote {
      margin: 0; padding: 0;
    }
    ul, ol { list-style: none; }
    img, svg, video, iframe { display: block; max-width: 100%; }
    button, input, select, textarea { font: inherit; color: inherit; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    /* ── Base ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    body {
      background: var(--paper);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 400;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    }

    h1, h2, h3, h4 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.25rem); }
    h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; }

    p + p { margin-top: 1rem; }

    /* ── Layout ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--maxw);
      margin-inline: auto;
      padding-inline: 1.25rem;
    }

    /* ── Page header ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .page-header {
      padding: 4rem 0 3.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }
    .page-name {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.0;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .page-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
    }
    .page-subtitle {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    /* ── Sections ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .portfolio-section {
      padding: 4rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }
    .portfolio-section:last-of-type {
      border-bottom: none;
      padding-bottom: 6rem;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.25rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .section-rule {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
      margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    }

    .section-intro {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--ink);
      max-width: 72ch;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    /* ── Screenshot cards ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .screenshot-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .screenshot-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    .screenshot-card {
      display: block;
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      background: var(--cream);
    }
    .screenshot-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--ink);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .screenshot-img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: top center;
      transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    }
    .screenshot-card:hover .screenshot-img {
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }
    .screenshot-caption {
      padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .screenshot-caption-arrow {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      text-transform: none;
      color: var(--ink);
      transition: transform 0.15s ease;
    }
    .screenshot-card:hover .screenshot-caption-arrow {
      transform: translateX(3px);
    }

    /* ── Embed stacks ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .embed-stack {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    /* ── Spotify embeds ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .spotify-embed-wrap {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .spotify-embed-wrap iframe {
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 152px;
    }

    /* ── Brand group labels (Advertising Scoring and Production) ────────── */
    .embed-brand-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }
    .embed-brand-row:first-child {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .embed-brand {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .embed-brand-detail {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ── YouTube embeds (responsive 16:9) ───────────────────────────────── */
    .video-wrap {
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 56.25%;
      height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--cream);
    }
    .video-wrap iframe {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-name">Eric Chan</h1>
      <p class="page-title">Selected Work</p>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Websites &nbsp;·&nbsp; Audio Engineering &nbsp;·&nbsp; Podcast &nbsp;·&nbsp; Advertising Scoring &amp; Production &nbsp;·&nbsp; Forget the G</p>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- 01 — WEBSITES -->
  <section class="portfolio-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">01</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Websites</h2>
      <hr class="section-rule" />
      <p class="section-intro">
        Inlet Wire is a podcast and media platform built for BC artists. The site features a
        clean, organized design that prioritizes discovery — with an extensive archive of
        episodes, direct links to all streaming platforms, full transcripts, and optimized
        metadata for search. I've implemented comprehensive SEO strategy including Google
        Analytics tracking, metadata optimization, structured tagging, and performance
        monitoring to ensure discoverability across search and discovery platforms. The design
        supports easy navigation across a growing catalog while maintaining a focused,
        professional aesthetic.
      </p>

      <div class="screenshot-grid">

        <a
          class="screenshot-card"
          href="https://inletwire.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          aria-label="Visit Inlet Wire — home"
        >
          <img
            class="screenshot-img"
            src="/images/portfolio/screenshot-home.png"
            alt="Inlet Wire — home page"
            width="1200"
            height="750"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="screenshot-caption">
            <span>inletwire.com — Home</span>
            <span class="screenshot-caption-arrow">↗</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a
          class="screenshot-card"
          href="https://inletwire.com/episodes/leah-abramson/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          aria-label="Visit Inlet Wire — episode page"
        >
          <img
            class="screenshot-img"
            src="/images/portfolio/screenshot-episodes.png"
            alt="Inlet Wire — episodes page"
            width="1200"
            height="750"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="screenshot-caption">
            <span>inletwire.com — Episode</span>
            <span class="screenshot-caption-arrow">↗</span>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- 02 — AUDIO ENGINEERING -->
  <section class="portfolio-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">02</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Audio Engineering</h2>
      <hr class="section-rule" />
      <p class="section-intro">
        I record, mix, and master for indie bands and artists across Taiwan, Hong Kong, and
        Macau, with a focus on experimental and alternative music. Day's Eye Records, my
        independent label founded in 2009, has released work across the region. In 2024, I
        established GenLab in Taichung as a dedicated studio and experimental music space. I
        work openly with artists to understand their creative vision, using arrangement,
        production techniques, and audio tools to realize what they're hearing. Artists and
        projects I've worked with have been recognized at the Macao TDM music awards and
        ranked in the top one hundred at the Freshmusic Awards across multiple years.
      </p>

      <div class="embed-stack">

        <div class="spotify-embed-wrap">
          <iframe
            src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/38eBrN1tq0EFYtu5GaVnrS?utm_source=generator"
            allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="spotify-embed-wrap">
          <iframe
            src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/086PLhjM6wRr9yPA0J7acF?utm_source=generator"
            allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="spotify-embed-wrap">
          <iframe
            src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/6XOceP7PhXNsL70lbL2L7y?utm_source=generator"
            allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- 03 — PODCAST — INLET WIRE -->
  <section class="portfolio-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">03</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Podcast — Inlet Wire</h2>
      <hr class="section-rule" />
      <p class="section-intro">
        I host and produce the podcast Inlet Wire, featuring edited artist interviews with
        musicians and producers across British Columbia. I conduct each interview and shape
        the final episode through narration that bridges the conversation — guiding listeners
        through the dialogue without interpreting or overriding the guest's voice. Each
        episode is a focused, reflective exchange captured in the artist's own words, designed
        to let listeners connect with the BC music scene on their own terms.
      </p>

      <div class="spotify-embed-wrap" style="height:380px;">
        <iframe
          style="height:380px;"
          src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/1De8QSqbYa15p5gXO78PDl?utm_source=generator"
          allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
          loading="lazy"
        ></iframe>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- 04 — MUSIC SCORING -->
  <section class="portfolio-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">04</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Advertising Scoring and Production</h2>
      <hr class="section-rule" />
      <p class="section-intro">
        I've composed and produced music for advertising and video work across Taiwan and Hong
        Kong, partnering with agencies and producers on campaigns for major brands including
        Dyson, Mitsubishi, HSBC, KFC, and ViewSonic. My approach centers on understanding each
        client's vision and delivering music that serves the story — whether that's orchestral
        arrangements, electronic textures, or hybrid compositions. I perform vocals and
        instruments on tracks when it fits the project, handling both composition and
        post-production to ensure the final product matches the brief exactly.
      </p>

      <div class="embed-stack">

        <div class="embed-brand-row">
          <span class="embed-brand">HSBC</span>
          <span class="embed-brand-detail">Music mixing &nbsp;·&nbsp; Audio post production</span>
