  <!-- 05 — FORGET THE G -->
  <section class="portfolio-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">05</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Forget the G</h2>
      <hr class="section-rule" />
      <p class="section-intro">
        As the vocalist, guitarist, trumpet player, and core songwriter of Forget the G, I
        write all original music and lyrics and handle recording, mixing, and string
        arrangement for every release. The band has been awarded the Album Production Subsidy
        from the Cultural Affairs Bureau, Macau twice — recognition for the quality and
        ambition of the work. Forget the G has performed extensively across Asia through
        multiple tours, bringing the music to audiences well beyond the region where it was made.
      </p>

      <div class="embed-stack">

        <div class="spotify-embed-wrap">
          <iframe
            src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/1bMWv0d0Amlt0nC3DaQTKN?utm_source=generator"
            allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="spotify-embed-wrap">
          <iframe
